sourcesContent: import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { NgForm } from '@angular/forms'; import { Project } from '../../../models/project.model'; import { DataServiceService } from '../../../services/data-service.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-add-edit-project', templateUrl: './add-edit-project.component.html', styleUrls: ['./add-edit-project.component.css'] }) export class AddEditProjectComponent { newProject!: Project; constructor(private dataService: DataServiceService) { } onSubmit(form: NgForm) { } addProject(project: Project) { this.dataService.addProject(project); } }
